channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Philadelphia Eagles To Wear Kelly Green Throwback Uniforms Twice In 2024
item.description: The Philadelphia Eagles will wear their Kelly green throwback uniforms twice this season, including against the Jacksonville Jaguars on Nov. 3 and Dallas Cowboys on Dec. 29.

item.title: Argentina, Adidas Extend Kit Contract Until 2038
item.description: Extension of contract between Asociación del Fútbol Argentino and German sportswear company ensures Albiceleste will wear 3 Stripes for next 4 World Cups

item.title: MLS’s Vancouver Whitecaps Introduce New Indigenous History Month Logo
